Usage: setWhatIfDriveType [-help] <blackBoxCellName> -cell <cellName>
                          [-inputPin <libraryInputPin>] [-lib <libName>]
                          [-outputPin <libraryOutputPin>]
                          [-port <outputPortName>] [ -slew <value> [ -outputCap <value> ] ]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>              # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                                # (string, required)
-cell <cellName>                # Specifies the name of the cell
                                # (string, required)
-inputPin <libraryInputPin>     # Specifies the input or inout pin of the cell 
                                # (string, optional)
-lib <libName>                  # Specifies the name of the timing library
                                # (string, optional)
-outputCap <value>              # Creates timing arcs even if they are not
                                # defined in the timing library (float, optional)
-outputPin <libraryOutputPin>   # Specifies the output or inout pin of the
                                # library  (string, optional)
-port <outputPortName>          # Specifies the name of the output port
                                # (string, optional)
-slew <value>                   # Specifies the slew at the input of the driver
                                # cell (float, optional)